UndoableRemoteEventWrapper
public abstract class UndoableRemoteEvent<H extends UndoableRemoteEventHandler<?>>
extends RemoteEvent<H>

A special type of event which includes additional undo functionality to establish optimistic concurrency control. Do instantiate this class directly through the GWT.create(Class) method.

Oliver Schmid
